    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "Facebook scales images in the feed based on their original ratio. Landscape images appear wider; square images appear as squares. Facebook renders images at up to 2048px wide on high-density screens, so uploading at 1200px or above is recommended."
    },
